{"title":"GangrenaFournier iPad","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/General/GangrenaFournier iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"GANGRENA\\NDE FOURNIER","guid":"BlzxX2p_ynoSlP2QTg8ZEg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definición","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Fascitis necrotizante del periné, genitales y región perianal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Descrita por Jean Alfred Fournier, 1883 (dermatólogo francés)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Infección POLIMICROBIANA → sinergismo bacteriano","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Progresión FULMINANTE → puede avanzar 2-3 cm/hora","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Mortalidad actual 20-40% (hasta 50% en series antiguas)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"Incidencia 1.6/100.000 hombres/año (↑ en mayores)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"Relación hombre:mujer ~10:1","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"Edad media ~50-60 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"7","text":"MAYOR incidencia en adultos mayores e inmunocomprometidos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"7","text":"Factores de riesgo poblacionales → DM, OH crónico, obesidad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"0","text":"Etiología y\\Nmicrobiología","guid":"yby-K1Yza5Zjs1cZgGW-FA","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"POLIMICROBIANA\\Nen mayoría de casos","guid":"9l5PJznTPZb96oAOOJMsmA","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"Aerobios → E. coli (MÁS FRECUENTE), Klebsiella, Proteus","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"Anaerobios → Bacteroides, Clostridium, Peptostreptococcus","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"Gram (+) → Streptococcus, Staphylococcus aureus","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"14","text":"Promedio 3-5 microorganismos por cultivo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"13","text":"Origen de\\Nla infección","guid":"Dr4jHRNEcZJ4gMY_o_xnsw","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"Colorrectal (~30-50%) → abscesos perianales, fisuras, Ca recto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"19","text":"Urogenital (~20-40%) → estenosis uretral, ITU, orquiepididimitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"19","text":"Cutáneo (~20%) → trauma, heridas, inyecciones, piercings","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"19","text":"IDIOPÁTICO (~10%) → sin etiología identificable","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"0","text":"Factores\\Nde riesgo","guid":"cKoAWjYAa25-Z2M7Au0cag","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"DM → presente en 40-70% de casos\\N(PRINCIPAL)","guid":"UsIVOGRW6wiZofo0fxfBjw","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"Microangiopatía + disfunción inmune","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"ISGLT2 → reportes de casos (FDA warning 2018), riesgo absoluto bajo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"24","text":"Alcoholismo crónico → inmunosupresión + desnutrición","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"24","text":"Inmunosupresión → VIH, QT, corticoides, trasplante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"24","text":"Obesidad → humedad perineal, dificultad higiene","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"24","text":"Edad avanzada → inmunosenescencia + comorbilidades","guid":"_jyjPbMvxVo4fqhFWlwkjA","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"24","text":"Enfermedad renal crónica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"24","text":"Malignidad activa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"24","text":"Desnutrición y albúmina baja","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"Puerta de entrada → mucosa o piel perineal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"Infección polimicrobiana → sinergismo aerobio-anaerobio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"35","text":"Endarteritis obliterante → trombosis de vasos pequeños","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"35","text":"Isquemia tisular → facilita proliferación anaerobia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"35","text":"Necrosis fascial progresiva → planos fasciales (Colles, Dartos, Scarpa)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"35","text":"Gas subcutáneo → producido por anaerobios (CREPITACIÓN)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"35","text":"Respuesta inflamatoria sistémica → sepsis → FOM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"35","text":"CASCADA RÁPIDA: horas a días desde inicio hasta necrosis extensa","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"0","text":"Clínica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"Síntomas iniciales\\N(frecuentemente\\NINESPECÍFICOS)","guid":"60a1MevGUMmnRgFppIhEBQ","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"Dolor perineal/genital desproporcionado al examen","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"Eritema y edema perineal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"45","text":"Fiebre (puede estar ausente en inmunocomprometidos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"45","text":"Malestar general, decaimiento","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"44","text":"Progresión","guid":"","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"Induración y crepitación subcutánea → GAS (patognomónico)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"Necrosis cutánea → placas negruzas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"Secreción purulenta/fétida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"50","text":"Extensión a pared abdominal, muslos, retroperitoneo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"44","text":"Signos de ALARMA\\N(emergencia quirúrgica)","guid":"--Y-PhahPXhL6W9V09mm6w","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"Crepitación a la palpación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"Dolor desproporcionado → CLAVE DIAGNÓSTICA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"55","text":"Rápida progresión del eritema (marcar bordes con marcador)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"55","text":"Signos de sepsis/shock séptico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"55","text":"Bulas hemorrágicas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"44","text":"CONSIDERACIONES\\NGERIÁTRICAS","guid":"n69poCgUmvD20UNcQSEuOw","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"Presentación atípica → menos fiebre, menos dolor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"Delirium como primera manifestación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"Retraso diagnóstico frecuente en AM → MAYOR mortalidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"61","text":"Fragilidad + Fournier → mortalidad >50%","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"CLÍNICO → no retrasar cirugía por imágenes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"Laboratorio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"Hemograma → leucocitosis (o leucopenia en sepsis severa)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"PCR, procalcitonina → marcadores inflamatorios","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"Gases/lactato → acidosis metabólica, hiperlactatemia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"68","text":"Función renal → creatinina elevada = mal pronóstico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"68","text":"Albúmina → hipoalbuminemia = mal pronóstico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"68","text":"Hemocultivos + cultivo de tejido (SIEMPRE)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"66","text":"LRINEC Score\\N(Laboratory Risk Indicator\\Nfor Necrotizing Fasciitis)","guid":"FgLwvNNmBY1hDNXXnmRxiA","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"PCR >=150 mg/L → 4 puntos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"Leucocitos >25.000 → 2 puntos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"75","text":"Hemoglobina <11 → 2 puntos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"75","text":"Sodio <135 → 2 puntos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"75","text":"Creatinina >1.6 → 2 puntos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"75","text":"Glucosa >180 → 1 punto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"75","text":"Score >=6 → ALTA sospecha fascitis necrotizante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"75","text":"Score >=8 → diagnóstico altamente probable (VPP 93%)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"66","text":"Imágenes (NO\\Nretrasar cirugía)","guid":"3djMSXxCwa2UT2m6eDecIA","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Rx simple → gas subcutáneo (baja sensibilidad)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"TC con contraste → MEJOR estudio\\Nsi hay duda diagnóstica","guid":"uA8DTEayXBT1pzEdMrGlrA","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"Gas en tejidos blandos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"Engrosamiento fascial asimétrico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"86","text":"Ausencia de realce fascial (necrosis)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"86","text":"Extensión y profundidad del compromiso","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"84","text":"RNM → mayor sensibilidad pero requiere más tiempo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"84","text":"Ecografía → útil para abscesos superficiales, gas","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"0","text":"Scores\\Npronósticos","guid":"f44WndZMDAhcgn9z-ZIeNQ","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"FGSI (Fournier Gangrene Severity Index)\\N→ Laor 1995","guid":"hCZcYnXcx4n-BoFIqtjvJw","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"9 parámetros: T°, FC, FR, Na, K, Creatinina, Leucocitos, Hto, HCO3","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"94","text":"Cada parámetro 0-4 puntos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"94","text":"Score >9 → mortalidad ~75% / sobrevida ~22%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"94","text":"Score <=9 → sobrevida ~78%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"94","text":"AUC 0.90 (IC 95% 0.87-0.92) en metaanálisis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"94","text":"Sensibilidad 65-88% / Especificidad 70-100%","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"93","text":"UFGSI (Uludag FGSI)\\N→ Yilmazlar 2010","guid":"WgXUhK4sP2tPnRWRzV3oSg","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"FGSI + EDAD + extensión de la gangrena","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"Score >9 → 94% probabilidad de muerte","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"Score <=9 → 81% probabilidad de sobrevida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"101","text":"AUC 0.94 (IC 95% 0.92-0.96) → MAYOR que FGSI","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"106","parent":"93","text":"SFGSI (Simplified FGSI)\\N→ Lin 2013","guid":"2TMSgwUwItEZVva1knSSdg","children":[{"id":"107","parent":"106","text":"Solo 3 parámetros: creatinina, hematocrito, potasio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"106","text":"AUC 0.84 (IC 95% 0.80-0.87)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"106","text":"Más simple pero menos preciso","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"93","text":"FGMI (FG Mortality Index)\\N→ 2024","guid":"c5qXi3jttJKdIvbf8seJ6Q","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"Edad, creatinina, albúmina, % linfocitos, NLR","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"110","text":"Nuevo score en validación","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"93","text":"Charlson Comorbidity Index\\N→ útil como complemento","guid":"xqW54XLdmd0pDqH9Af6C6g","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"Mayor CCI → mayor mortalidad en FG","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"Cada punto CCI → OR mortalidad 1.2","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"93","text":"FGSI por cada\\Npunto adicional","guid":"ihKqsLOMX2b8GESeNzqaJA","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"OR mortalidad 1.14","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"116","text":"OR ingreso UCI 1.3","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"116","text":"+1.1 días de hospitalización","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"0","text":"Manejo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"PRINCIPIOS\\NFUNDAMENTALES","guid":"sL1fFf7bJMfqfgyksFG3AQ","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"1. RESUCITACIÓN agresiva (ABC, fluidos, vasopresores si shock)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"2. ATB empírico de AMPLIO ESPECTRO precoz","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"3. DEBRIDAMIENTO QUIRÚRGICO urgente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"121","text":"4. Reintervenciones seriadas (second look 24-48h)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"126","parent":"120","text":"Antibioterapia\\Nempírica","guid":"s5M8iW4DHmPG16WpswYKhg","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"Esquema amplio espectro → aerobios + anaerobios + gram(+)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"Opción 1: Piperacilina/Tazobactam + Vancomicina + Clindamicina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"126","text":"Opción 2: Meropenem + Vancomicina + Clindamicina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"126","text":"Opción 3: Ceftriaxona + Metronidazol + Clindamicina (recurso limitado)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"126","text":"Clindamicina → CLAVE por efecto antitoxina (inhibe síntesis proteica)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"126","text":"Ajustar según cultivos y antibiograma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"126","text":"Duración: hasta control de infección + 48-72h afebril post-desbridamiento final","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"120","text":"Cirugía","guid":"","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"DEBRIDAMIENTO AMPLIO → hasta tejido sano (sangrado activo)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"134","text":"Sin preservar estética → VIDA sobre cosmética","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"134","text":"Reintervención a las 24-48h (SECOND LOOK obligatorio)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"134","text":"Promedio 3-4 desbridamientos por paciente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"134","text":"Colostomía derivativa → si compromiso perianal extenso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"134","text":"Cistostomía suprapúbica → si compromiso uretral/peneano","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"141","parent":"120","text":"Cuidados\\Nintensivos","guid":"_u7YPGl1YqJDQdIkpApE0g","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"Monitorización hemodinámica continua","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"141","text":"Soporte ventilatorio si FOM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"141","text":"Nutrición precoz (enteral preferida)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"141","text":"Control metabólico estricto (DM)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"141","text":"Manejo del dolor (EVA/PAINAD en AM)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"141","text":"Prevención delirium (protocolo ABCDEF)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"120","text":"Terapias\\Ncomplementarias","guid":"bdv_G38O5bfLBcA8D8iEiw","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"VAC (Vacuum Assisted Closure) → acelera granulación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"Oxígeno hiperbárico → evidencia limitada, puede ser complemento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"Miel de Manuka/apósitos bioactivos → uso creciente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"120","text":"Reconstrucción\\N(fase tardía)","guid":"15Yd3OGwe8g0VOdExp9zPQ","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"Cierre por segunda intención","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"Injertos de piel","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"Colgajos miocutáneos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"152","text":"Reconstrucción escrotal/vulvar","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"157","parent":"0","text":"Pronóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"Mortalidad global 20-40%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"157","text":"Factores de\\NMAL pronóstico","guid":"di1z8eAPolgG2ckVSqr6aQ","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"Edad avanzada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"Retraso en cirugía >24h desde diagnóstico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"159","text":"Extensión a pared abdominal/retroperitoneo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"159","text":"Sepsis/shock séptico al ingreso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"159","text":"FOM al ingreso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"159","text":"FGSI >9 / UFGSI >9","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"159","text":"Albúmina baja al ingreso y al final","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"159","text":"Creatinina elevada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"159","text":"Necesidad de UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"159","text":"DM mal controlada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"159","text":"FRAGILIDAD (CFS >=5) en adulto mayor","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"157","text":"Factores\\NPROTECTORES","guid":"ifakevoOX8CyDLuO-6jgRA","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"Diagnóstico precoz (<24h síntomas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"171","text":"Desbridamiento agresivo temprano","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"171","text":"ATB adecuado precoz","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"171","text":"Bajo CCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"171","text":"Buen estado nutricional","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"177","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClínicas","guid":"8ELfYTPHNcwFD9C9HK-9aQ","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"DOLOR DESPROPORCIONADO al examen físico = SIEMPRE pensar fascitis necrotizante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"177","text":"CREPITACIÓN subcutánea = gas = NO esperar imágenes → cirugía YA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"177","text":"LRINEC >=6 → alta sospecha, pero score bajo NO descarta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"177","text":"NUNCA retrasar cirugía por imágenes en alta sospecha clínica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"177","text":"Clindamicina SIEMPRE en esquema ATB → efecto antitoxina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"177","text":"En AM: presentación atípica (sin fiebre, sin dolor intenso, delirium)","guid":"_rz-ZvYOma__fPzPYkKFiQ","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"177","text":"Retraso diagnóstico en AM → principal causa de mayor mortalidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"177","text":"ISGLT2 → FDA warning 2018, valorar suspensión temporal en infección perineal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"177","text":"FGSI/UFGSI al ingreso → estratificar y comunicar pronóstico a familia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"177","text":"Second look OBLIGATORIO a 24-48h → no dar por terminado con 1 desbridamiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"177","text":"Colostomía derivativa PRECOZ si compromiso perianal extenso → reduce contaminación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"177","text":"Albúmina baja = factor independiente de mortalidad → suplementar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"177","text":"En AM frágil: discutir proporcionalidad terapéutica con equipo y familia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"191","parent":"0","text":"VER\\NTAMBIÉN","guid":"wVForbGJj9lPrAGLK-gZCw","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"→ Sepsis y Shock Séptico (Medicina Intensiva)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"191","text":"→ Infecciones de Piel y Partes Blandas (Infectología)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"191","text":"→ Delirium en UCI (Geriatría)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"191","text":"→ Fragilidad y Pronóstico (Valoración Geriátrica)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"191","text":"→ Proporcionalidad Terapéutica (Bioética)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"191","text":"→ Antibioterapia Empírica (Farmacología)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"191","text":"→ Sepsis (MedicinaIntensiva)","guid":"BDlgmWiObZG0y93Z4D-mPA","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"191","text":"→ Delirium (Geriatría)","guid":"B_TtIMBE5KRqaswr8YUwvA","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"191","text":"→ Fragilidad (Valoración)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"191","text":"→ IPPB (Infectología)","guid":"dHxJ2XE2i347sC9wOuxk7A","children":[]}]},{"id":"202","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"1. Bowen D, et al. Fournier's gangrene: a review of predictive scoring systems and practical guide for patient management. Ther Adv Urol. 2024;16:20499361241238521.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"2. Adli G, et al. Comparing scoring systems for Fournier gangrenes in predicting morbidity and mortality. Arab J Urol. 2024;34(9):102673.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"202","text":"3. Tufano A, et al. The Value of Fournier's Gangrene Scoring Systems on Admission to Predict Mortality: A Systematic Review and Meta-Analysis. J Pers Med. 2023;13(9):1283.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"202","text":"4. Hauser N, et al. FGSI and CCI Predict Mortality, ICU Admission, and Length of Hospital Stay in FG: Analysis of 264 Patients. Cureus. 2024;16(12):e75281.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"202","text":"5. Yilmazlar T, et al. Fournier's gangrene: an analysis of 80 patients and a novel scoring system. Tech Coloproctol. 2010;14(3):217-23.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"202","text":"6. Laor E, et al. Outcome prediction in patients with Fournier's gangrene. J Urol. 1995;154(1):89-92.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"202","text":"7. Eke N. Fournier's gangrene: a review of 1726 cases. Br J Surg. 2000;87(6):718-28.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"202","text":"8. Wong CH, et al. The LRINEC score: a tool for distinguishing necrotizing fasciitis from other soft tissue infections. Crit Care Med. 2004;32(7):1535-41.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":210,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"GangrenaFournier iPad","id":"map_766","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"GangrenaFournier iPad"}